  "id": "class:bard#disciple_of_the_forked_tongue_vishkanya",
  "name": "Disciple of the Forked Tongue (Vishkanya)",
  "tags": ["archetype", "bard"],
  "description": {
    "text": "Studied in venomous words as well as venomous blood, a disciple of the forked tongue knows just the right phrase to slowly poison the soul. His voice can sink deep into his victims\u0027 hearts, destroying friendships and devouring the mind. The disciple of the forked tongue is an archetype of the bard class available to vishkanya characters."
